Experiment No: 5
Aim: Design an XML document to store information about a student in an engineering
college affiliated to VTU. The information must include USN, Name, and Name ofthe College, Branch, Year of Joining, and email id. Make up sample data for 3students. Create a CSS style sheet and use it to display the document.
<?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" href="6.css" ?> <!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<h1> STUDENTS DESCRIPTION </h1> </head>
<students>
